obo:IAO_0000115  a  owl:AnnotationProperty .

[ a                      owl:Axiom ;
  rdfs:comment           "Evidence statement (PMID:26060020): Despite probably being completely dimeric in the cell membrane, LET-23 activation remains strictly dependent on\naddition of LIN-3 (Fig. 1e and Supplementary Fig. 2c,d). We\nexpressed full-length LET-23 in D. melanogaster Schneider-2 (S2)\ncells as a null background and showed that LIN-3EGF is sufficient\nto activate the heterologously expressed receptor." ;
